<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AutoGram v2 — Cloud Free Stack</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Cabinet+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap');
  :root {
    --bg: #0c0e0f;
    --surface: #141618;
    --surface2: #1c1f21;
    --border: #272b2e;
    --accent: #00e5a0;
    --accent2: #00b4ff;
    --accent3: #ffb800;
    --accent4: #ff5f7e;
    --text: #dde2e6;
    --muted: #5a6370;
    --ok: #00e5a0;
    --warn: #ffb800;
    --danger: #ff5f7e;
    --next: #00b4ff;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Cabinet Grotesk', sans-serif;
    padding: 48px 28px;
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .header-top { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  h1 {
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
  .version-pill {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    background: rgba(0,229,160,0.12);
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,160,0.25);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .sub {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  /* FORK BANNER */
  .fork-banner {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,255,0.25);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .fork-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .fork-body { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: #7aaecc; }
  .fork-body strong { color: var(--accent2); }

  /* PROGRESS BAR */
  .progress-wrap {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .progress-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 13px; }
  .progress-label .pct { font-weight: 700; color: var(--ok); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; }
  .progress-bar { height: 6px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent2), var(--accent));
    border-radius: 3px;
    width: 70%;
  }
  .progress-phases {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .phase {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6px 4px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .phase-done { background: rgba(0,229,160,0.1); color: var(--ok); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,160,0.2); }
  .phase-active { background: rgba(0,180,255,0.15); color: var(--accent2); border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,255,0.3); }
  .phase-pending { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* STATS */
  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .stat {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat .val {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .stat .lbl {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* STACK COMPARISON */
  .stack-compare {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .stack-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
  }
  .stack-box.old { border-top: 2px solid var(--muted); }
  .stack-box.new { border-top: 2px solid var(--accent); }
  .stack-title {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .stack-title.old { color: var(--muted); }
  .stack-title.new { color: var(--accent); }
  .stack-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 7px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .stack-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .stack-row .lbl { color: var(--muted); }
  .stack-row .val-old { color: #888; text-decoration: line-through; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; }
  .stack-row .val-new { color: var(--accent); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }

  h2 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 32px 0 14px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }
  .section { margin-bottom: 32px; }

  /* ITEMS */
  .item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 13px 16px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .item-icon { font-size: 17px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .item-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .item-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .item-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .item-badge { margin-left: auto; flex-shrink: 0; padding-left: 12px; }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .badge-ok { background: rgba(0,229,160,0.12); color: var(--ok); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,160,0.25); }
  .badge-warn { background: rgba(255,184,0,0.12); color: var(--warn); border: 1px solid rgba(255,184,0,0.25); }
  .badge-next { background: rgba(0,180,255,0.12); color: var(--accent2); border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,255,0.25); }
  .badge-skip { background: rgba(90,99,112,0.12); color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid rgba(90,99,112,0.2); }
  .badge-new { background: rgba(255,184,0,0.12); color: var(--accent3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,184,0,0.25); }
  .badge-refactor { background: rgba(255,95,126,0.1); color: var(--accent4); border: 1px solid rgba(255,95,126,0.2); }

  /* FILE TREE */
  .tree {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #5a6370;
  }
  .tree .folder { color: var(--accent3); }
  .tree .file-py { color: var(--accent); }
  .tree .file-cfg { color: var(--accent2); }
  .tree .file-env { color: var(--accent4); }
  .tree .done::after { content: ' ✓'; color: var(--ok); }
  .tree .partial::after { content: ' ~'; color: var(--warn); }
  .tree .changed { color: var(--accent4); }
  .tree .changed::after { content: ' ← direfactor'; color: var(--accent4); font-size: 10px; opacity: 0.7; }

  /* NOTES */
  .note {
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 12px 0;
  }
  .note-info { background: rgba(0,180,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(0,180,255,0.2); color: #7aaecc; }
  .note-warn { background: rgba(255,184,0,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,184,0,0.2); color: #c49a40; }
  .note-ok { background: rgba(0,229,160,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,160,0.2); color: #3daa7a; }

  code {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    background: var(--surface2);
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* FREE COST TABLE */
  .cost-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin: 8px 0 16px;
  }
  .cost-table th {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0 12px 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .cost-table td {
    padding: 9px 12px 9px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    vertical-align: middle;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .cost-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .free-pill {
    background: rgba(0,229,160,0.1);
    color: var(--ok);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,160,0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .limit-pill {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="header-top">
    <h1>Auto<span>Gram</span></h1>
    <div class="version-pill">v2 · CLOUD FREE</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sub">PROGRESS REKAP · 15 MEI 2026</div>
</div>

<!-- FORK BANNER -->
<div class="fork-banner">
  <div class="fork-icon">⑂</div>
  <div class="fork-body">
    <strong>Fork dari v1 (lokal) → v2 (cloud gratis)</strong><br>
    Semua logika pipeline tetap sama. Yang berubah hanya layer AI dan infrastruktur: Ollama + ComfyUI lokal diganti ke <strong>Groq API + Pollinations.ai</strong>, dan scheduler dipindah ke <strong>Oracle Cloud Free VM</strong>. PC tidak perlu menyala lagi.
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROGRESS -->
<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-label">
    <span>Overall Progress</span>
    <span class="pct">70% — Refactor + Deploy</span>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-bar">
    <div class="progress-fill"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="progress-phases">
    <div class="phase phase-done">1 · ENGINES</div>
    <div class="phase phase-done">2 · PIPELINE</div>
    <div class="phase phase-active">3 · REFACTOR API</div>
    <div class="phase phase-pending">4 · DEPLOY VM</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="val" style="color:var(--ok)">0</div>
    <div class="lbl">BIAYA / BULAN</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="val" style="color:var(--accent2)">2</div>
    <div class="lbl">FILE DIREFACTOR</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="val" style="color:var(--accent3)">∞</div>
    <div class="lbl">UPTIME (VM)</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="val" style="color:var(--accent)">24/7</div>
    <div class="lbl">PC BEBAS MATI</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STACK COMPARISON -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>🔀 Perubahan Stack</h2>
  <div class="stack-compare">
    <div class="stack-box old">
      <div class="stack-title old">v1 · LOKAL</div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">LLM</span><span class="val-old">Ollama llama3.1</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">QA Model</span><span class="val-old">qwen2.5-coder:14b</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">Image Gen</span><span class="val-old">ComfyUI + SDXL</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">Server</span><span class="val-old">PC harus nyala</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">Biaya</span><span class="val-old">Listrik + HDD</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stack-box new">
      <div class="stack-title new">v2 · CLOUD GRATIS</div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">LLM</span><span class="val-new">Groq API (llama3)</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">QA Model</span><span class="val-new">Groq API (mixtral)</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">Image Gen</span><span class="val-new">Pollinations.ai</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">Server</span><span class="val-new">Oracle Cloud Free VM</span></div>
      <div class="stack-row"><span class="lbl">Biaya</span><span class="val-new">Rp 0 / bulan</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <table class="cost-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>LAYANAN</th>
        <th>DIGUNAKAN UNTUK</th>
        <th>LIMIT GRATIS</th>
        <th>STATUS</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Groq API</strong></td>
        <td>Caption + QA scoring</td>
        <td><span class="limit-pill">~14.400 req/hari</span></td>
        <td><span class="free-pill">GRATIS</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Pollinations.ai</strong></td>
        <td>Image 1080×1080px</td>
        <td><span class="limit-pill">Unlimited, no key</span></td>
        <td><span class="free-pill">GRATIS</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Oracle Cloud VM</strong></td>
        <td>Jalankan scheduler 24/7</td>
        <td><span class="limit-pill">ARM 4c/24GB, forever</span></td>
        <td><span class="free-pill">GRATIS</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Telegram Bot</strong></td>
        <td>Notifikasi</td>
        <td><span class="limit-pill">Unlimited</span></td>
        <td><span class="free-pill">GRATIS</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- SUDAH SELESAI (v1 carried over) -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>✅ Selesai & Dipertahankan dari v1</h2>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🏗️</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Project Structure & Environment</div>
      <div class="item-desc">Folder, Python 3.13 venv, .gitignore, config.yaml. Tambahkan <code>GROQ_API_KEY</code> ke .env.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🗄️</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Database — <code>core/database.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Tidak ada perubahan. SQLite 4 tabel tetap dipakai.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🔍</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Trend Engine — <code>engines/trend_engine.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Tidak ada perubahan. Google Trends scraping tidak pakai LLM lokal.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">📤</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Post Engine — <code>engines/post_engine.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Tidak ada perubahan. instagrapi + session + dry_run logic tetap sama.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🔄</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Pipeline Orchestrator — <code>core/pipeline.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Logic flow tidak berubah. Hanya dependency ke engine yang direfactor.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">⏰</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Scheduler — <code>core/scheduler.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">APScheduler + random interval 44–52 jam. Tidak berubah — tinggal dipindah ke Oracle VM.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">📬</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Telegram Notifier — <code>core/notifier.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Bot @autogram_superchronos_bot aktif dan sudah tertest.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-ok">DONE</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">📱</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Warmup Akun @superchronos.ai</div>
      <div class="item-desc">Hari ke-1 dari 14. 2 post manual sudah ada. Lanjut warmup sambil refactor berjalan.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-warn">WARMUP</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- YANG DIREFACTOR -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>🔧 Perlu Direfactor</h2>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">✍️</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Content Engine — <code>engines/content_engine.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Ganti <code>ollama.generate(model="llama3.1"...)</code> → <code>groq.chat.completions.create(model="llama-3.1-8b-instant"...)</code>. Install <code>pip install groq</code>.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-refactor">REFACTOR</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🔍</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">QA Engine — <code>engines/qa_engine.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Ganti <code>qwen2.5-coder:14b</code> di Ollama → <code>mixtral-8x7b-32768</code> di Groq. Format response tetap JSON scoring.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-refactor">REFACTOR</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🎨</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Visual Engine — <code>engines/visual_engine.py</code></div>
      <div class="item-desc">Ganti ComfyUI API → HTTP GET ke <code>https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/{prompt}?width=1080&height=1080</code>. Tidak butuh API key.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-refactor">REFACTOR</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SELANJUTNYA -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>⬜ Selanjutnya</h2>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🔑</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Daftar & Ambil Groq API Key</div>
      <div class="item-desc">Daftar di <code>console.groq.com</code> → buat API key → tambahkan <code>GROQ_API_KEY=...</code> ke .env</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-next">NEXT</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🔧</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Refactor 3 Engine (content, qa, visual)</div>
      <div class="item-desc">~30 menit kerja. Groq SDK mirip OpenAI, mudah dimigrasi. Pollinations cukup satu baris <code>requests.get()</code>.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-next">NEXT</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🔗</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Integrasi Notifier ke Pipeline</div>
      <div class="item-desc">Tambahkan <code>notify_success()</code> / <code>notify_fail()</code> di <code>core/pipeline.py</code>.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-next">NEXT</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">☁️</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Setup Oracle Cloud Free VM</div>
      <div class="item-desc">Daftar Oracle Cloud → buat VM ARM (Always Free) → install Python, clone repo, setup systemd service untuk auto-restart.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-next">NEXT</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <div class="item-icon">🧪</div>
    <div class="item-body">
      <div class="item-title">Test Full Pipeline di VM (dry_run=True)</div>
      <div class="item-desc">Jalankan pipeline dari VM, pastikan semua API call berhasil, Telegram notif masuk, log ke DB berjalan.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item-badge"><span class="badge badge-next">NEXT</span></div>
  </div>

